1
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:23,000
Officer Chen.

2
00:00:23,079 --> 00:00:23,559
Officer Chen.

3
00:00:23,559 --> 00:00:24,800
Officer Chen, we've got the details.

4
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,160
The victim's name is Wang Danni.

5
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,399
She taught at Lishan Welfare Academy.

6
00:00:27,480 --> 00:00:28,719
We've confirmed the suspects involved.

7
00:00:28,719 --> 00:00:29,800
Most of them are Heyisheng members.

8
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:30,679
Witnesses say

9
00:00:30,679 --> 00:00:31,800
a core Heyisheng member,

10
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,039
Liang Zhiqiang, had direct contact

11
00:00:34,039 --> 00:00:35,640
with the corpse after it fell.

12
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,479
He's now our prime suspect.

13
00:00:38,679 --> 00:00:39,240
Good.

14
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:41,359
Seal off the scene first

15
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,479
for further investigation.

16
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:48,960
Where's Xie Guanhong?

17
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:50,880
I don't know.

18
00:00:51,079 --> 00:00:52,119
I don't know anything.

19
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:54,719
I don't know!

20
00:00:56,079 --> 00:00:56,679
Brother Qiang.

21
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:58,039
What are you doing, Brother Qiang?

22
00:00:58,799 --> 00:01:00,359
You think you're being loyal?

23
00:01:01,119 --> 00:01:03,359
Let me show you what loyalty really means.

24
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:09,280
I'll break every bone in your body,

25
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,519
until you tell me.

26
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,159
Hey, Ah Qiang.

27
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,359
Where are you?

28
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:24,400
Kill Xie Guanhong,

29
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,560
and I'll turn myself in.

30
00:01:25,879 --> 00:01:26,719
Hey!

31
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,799
Stop right there!

32
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:32,840
Freeze!

33
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:06,239
You wanna fight me on my own turf?

34
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,920
You'll never win.

35
00:02:20,879 --> 00:02:22,319
You murderer!

36
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,599
I'm beyond redemption.

37
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,800
Kill me.

38
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,599
Kill me!

39
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,159
The flowers look gorgeous today.

40
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:05,360
Uncle Xiang, put it on my tab.

41
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:07,120
Brat.

42
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,520
Hey!

43
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:11,759
Stand right there.

44
00:03:12,280 --> 00:03:13,360
Hands behind your head.

45
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,960
Heyisheng's been acting up lately.

46
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:20,560
You and Ahong better watch your backs.

47
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,360
I don't want anyone missing at the graves.

48
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:24,120
With a hometown buddy watching my back,

49
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:24,919
what have I got to fear?

50
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:27,439
What goes around comes around.

51
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:28,800
I'm heading off.

52
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:29,759
Go on, get out of here.

53
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:13,439
Ahong!

54
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,479
What are you doing?

55
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,639
If I kill you, I'll be the boss!

56
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,759
I'm sorry, Brother Long.

57
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,160
Brother Long!

58
00:04:30,839 --> 00:04:31,920
I know I was wrong.

59
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:58,959
Brother Long was the boss of Heyisheng.

60
00:04:59,360 --> 00:05:02,199
He treated you two like his own children.

61
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:03,279
But tonight, he's dead.

62
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,240
You were the only one left at the scene.

63
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,319
So tell me,

64
00:05:06,319 --> 00:05:07,839
what happened to him?

65
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:10,199
Brother Long!

66
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,680
Brother Long!

67
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,480
Brother Long!

68
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:15,920
Brother Long!

69
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:18,839
Run!

70
00:05:18,839 --> 00:05:20,000
Qiang, run!

71
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:23,920
Call an ambulance!

72
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,800
Call an ambulance!

73
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:25,800
It was an accident.

74
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,839
It was an accident!

75
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:31,399
Brother Long!

76
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,279
Freeze!

77
00:05:34,279 --> 00:05:34,879
Hands up!

78
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,680
I didn't see anything.

79
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:39,920
Are you out of your mind?

80
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,920
Do you know how long you'll be locked up?

81
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:43,879
For life!

82
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:45,519
If you go to prison, what about Bao Jiao?

83
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,800
What did you promise me back then?

84
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,639
You said everything would be fine.

85
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:09,240
Liang Zhiqiang, for Intentional Injury,

86
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:11,240
gets 20 years of fixed-term imprisonment,

87
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,439
effective immediately.

88
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:20,920
Didn't you promise to marry me?

89
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,959
How can you marry me now?

90
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:23,319
You liar!

91
00:06:23,439 --> 00:06:24,319
I'm not a liar.

92
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:24,920
I promised you.

93
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:25,600
I said I'd marry you.

94
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,639
And I will.

95
00:06:26,639 --> 00:06:27,439
20 years.

96
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,519
Do you understand?

97
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:31,319
That's 20 whole years!

98
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:39,120
Ahong, take good care of her.

99
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:59,360
And now,

100
00:06:59,399 --> 00:07:02,560
let's wish the couple lifelong happiness,

101
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,079
and a baby soon!

102
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,360
Consummate the marriage right here!

103
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,079
Yeah!

104
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:13,800
Kiss! Kiss!

105
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,639
What's this?

106
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:33,279
You think a ring is enough to marry me?

107
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:35,120
I am Bao Jiao!

108
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,040
When I get married,

109
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,519
it's got to be a proper, grand wedding.

110
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:40,399
I'll only marry in style and glory.

111
00:07:40,399 --> 00:07:41,160
You understand?

112
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:42,160
Of course.

113
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,279
Liang Zhiqiang's woman

114
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,959
deserves to get married in glorious style.

115
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,120
That's right.

116
00:07:58,519 --> 00:08:05,160
Ma'am!

117
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:18,279
Dragon Head

118
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:25,319
Brother Bao

119
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,600
What are you doing?

120
00:08:30,519 --> 00:08:31,319
Bye-bye.

121
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,519
Okay.

122
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,720
Are you scared?

123
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,360
No, I'm not.

124
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,000
So adorable.

125
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:51,840
Let's go.

126
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:51,240
Boss.
